OL,3,CPC sacked for 'appalling' racist
OL,4,Cremark about colleague
OL,6,FA police officer who made an
OL,7,F'appalling' racist remark about a
OL,8,Fcolleague has been sacked.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) say PC
OL,11,FScott Dixon used a racist term about a
OL,12,Fblack officer at Bury police station
OL,13,Flast summer, when officers were
OL,14,Fdiscussing an ongoing professional
OL,15,Fstandards investigation into alleged
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory behaviour.
