OL,3,CPC sacked for 'appalling' racist
OL,4,Cremark about colleague
OL,6,FGMP said there is 'no place for
OL,7,Fdiscriminatory behaviour', even if it
OL,8,Fis intended as 'banter'.
OL,10,FAssistant Chief Constable Matt Boyle
OL,11,Fsaid: "What PC Dixon said was
OL,12,Fappalling, which he accepts.
OL,14,F"We have absolutely no tolerance for
OL,15,Fany such deplorable language or
OL,16,Fdiscrimination anywhere in GMP.
OL,18,F"PC Dixon's reaction to our internal
OL,19,Finvestigation was totally at odds with
OL,20,Four response to the serious initial
OL,21,Fallegations of discrimination.
