OL,3,CPC sacked for 'appalling' racist
OL,4,Cremark about colleague
OL,6,F"While our Professional Standards
OL,7,FDirectorate made immediate enquiries
OL,8,Fto thoroughly investigate, PC Dixon
OL,9,Fdecided to display the behaviour we're
OL,10,Fso keenly rooting out.
OL,12,F"There can be no excuse for using
OL,13,Fracist words. We were absolutely clear
OL,14,Fwhen we adopted the Angiolini
OL,15,Frecommendations a year ago that being
OL,16,Fan anti-discriminatory organisation
OL,17,Fmeans no tolerance to any such
OL,18,Fbehaviour or language in our police
OL,19,Fforce. This is the least our officers
OL,20,Fand the public rightly expect."
